{"tid":742314,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"各位有無睇過呢個廣州嘅Game評團隊 Gamker？","createTime":"2018-07-14T12:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T14:39:02.000Z","uid":44827,"like":22,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"161947c1c1fca1cb2569d9aadb5c3fc51dcbd85e","tid":742314,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"因為小弟英文唔太好，Game Review好多時都係睇返中文嘅，我都會睇香港嘅平民，3i之類，可能係片長問題，比起佢地，我覺得呢個Gamker嘅講評更加有深度認真，同埋有共鳴，每隻Game閒閒地都20-30分鐘左右。<br />\n<br />\nGamker 個主持肥仔好似係曾經開發過Game，所以佢地對Game嘅瞭解會比一般玩家深好多<br />\n佢地好多時評Game唔會淨係講好玩定唔好玩<br />\n而係好多時會有更加深刻嘅體驗講俾玩家<br />\n例如由生活、社會、甚至係哲學角度去欣賞一隻Game<br />\n同埋仲會講下有關成個遊戲界的發展之類<br />\n佢雖然係大陸嘅團隊，但Upload上youtube嘅新片（大部分）會專登用返繁體字幕<br />\n如果唔係極其對普通話、大陸野敏感嘅人，我真係誠心推薦。<br />\n<br />\n例如評Detroit Become Human會講下人工智能發展：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vIQKAE-E8sA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvIQKAE-E8sA&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=07284ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vIQKAE-E8sA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評汪達與巨像會探討埋人點面對孤獨：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Ly3jf44Dmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Ly3jf44Dmo&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bfd4e029\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Ly3jf44Dmo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由上古捲軸講講RPG嘅起源同唔同主流RPG嘅分野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3zcwvP0CXoc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3zcwvP0CXoc&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6e2ee88e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3zcwvP0CXoc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至會解釋好多人都一知半解嘅FPS（幀數），不過因為條片舊啲同比較資料性，所以唔會話好搞笑，但睇得出佢地好有心咁做。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O5w9odp3n48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO5w9odp3n48&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=14e0ee2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O5w9odp3n48</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多片都好有心機，例如Xenoblade 2嘅Game評，睇過佢同平民就知兩個團隊對遊戲嘅理解係差天共地。唔想因為佢係講普通話就埋沒左佢地喺香港嘅知名度，所以想俾多啲人識，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"94e011b2d6d68292306d2d5657539256d66cafdc","tid":742314,"uid":46390,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"有睇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢真係講得好好，一隻game會好多方面探討"},{"pid":"5e7464cb4546be7c4b5b5541500041cdca286baf","tid":742314,"uid":44827,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"94e011b2d6d68292306d2d5657539256d66cafdc","tid":742314,"uid":46390,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"有睇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢真係講得好好，一隻game會好多方面探討"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"巴打識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到隔離Post講敖廠長，我覺得Gamker都值得多啲人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a82cb39848d1e050a7f869c4fd1eb70fceee8c","tid":742314,"uid":44827,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"Post返平民同Gamker評 Xenoblade 2嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n平民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ucSiXMgGvSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FucSiXMgGvSQ&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fc602b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ucSiXMgGvSQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGamker <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DPiZV1v006o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDPiZV1v006o&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgwef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ea2aa743\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DPiZV1v006o</a>"},{"pid":"994eff1ab295e7fb4e85810cb5ea5a18b312e14e","tid":742314,"uid":46390,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"但又公道咁講，平民好似得2個人<br />\ngamker係一個團隊，人力物力都冇得比，遊戲既專業知識更加冇得比"},{"pid":"097798cb4fca632a488a694ae89f3ea59caebafd","tid":742314,"uid":44827,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"994eff1ab295e7fb4e85810cb5ea5a18b312e14e","tid":742314,"uid":46390,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"但又公道咁講，平民好似得2個人<br />\ngamker係一個團隊，人力物力都冇得比，遊戲既專業知識更加冇得比"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"其實我都有Keep住睇平民，佢地除左Xenoblade 2嘅Game評其他Game都評得無乜問題<br />\n只係會覺得，點解一隻Game都未玩到戲肉又未瞭解曬就趕住出Review，好肉酸<br />\n可能嘅話其實我都想佢地重新出過一次，以免一次嘅失誤勸退好多人<br />\n<br />\n所以我先想俾多啲人識Gamker，相信有多啲競爭，香港嘅Game評人會做得更加好"},{"pid":"85f936c728946df2edd9031a3804d9250c526be0","tid":742314,"uid":130568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"097798cb4fca632a488a694ae89f3ea59caebafd","tid":742314,"uid":44827,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"994eff1ab295e7fb4e85810cb5ea5a18b312e14e","tid":742314,"uid":46390,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"但又公道咁講，平民好似得2個人<br />\ngamker係一個團隊，人力物力都冇得比，遊戲既專業知識更加冇得比"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"其實我都有Keep住睇平民，佢地除左Xenoblade 2嘅Game評其他Game都評得無乜問題<br />\n只係會覺得，點解一隻Game都未玩到戲肉又未瞭解曬就趕住出Review，好肉酸<br />\n可能嘅話其實我都想佢地重新出過一次，以免一次嘅失誤勸退好多人<br />\n<br />\n所以我先想俾多啲人識Gamker，相信有多啲競爭，香港嘅Game評人會做得更加好"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"Xenoblade 2、FFXV、No Man Sky都係黑歷史<br />\n平民係得Gundam遊戲叫做得比較好，因為佢地係因了解而恨，恨鐵不成鋼<br />\n其他Game多數係唔了解就屌咗先"},{"pid":"bece2debfff5611c46517d165830098fcd29b957","tid":742314,"uid":130568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"85f936c728946df2edd9031a3804d9250c526be0","tid":742314,"uid":130568,"like":3,"d